queries.user_query: What was the total trading volume for technology stocks last month?
queries.sql_generated:
WITH LatestData AS (
    SELECT
        MAX(year) AS max_year,
        MAX(month) AS max_month
    FROM visualization_main_data
),
TargetMonth AS (
    SELECT
        CASE
            WHEN max_month = 1 THEN max_year - 1
            ELSE max_year
        END AS target_year,
        CASE
            WHEN max_month = 1 THEN 12
            ELSE max_month - 1
        END AS target_month
    FROM LatestData
)
SELECT
    SUM(vmd.quantity) AS total_trading_volume
FROM
    visualization_main_data AS vmd
JOIN
    TargetMonth AS tm ON vmd.year = tm.target_year AND vmd.month = tm.target_month
WHERE
    vmd.sector = 'Technology';
